# Marketplace core

- Multi-vendor marketplace: bounded contexts in `services/` (Identity, Catalog, Cart-Order, Inventory, Payment, Notification, Gateway).
- One PostgreSQL database per service; no shared tables across services.
- Async integration via RabbitMQ events; HTTP via Ocelot + Nginx.
- Work in sprint order (infra → gateway → domain → UI). Track work as GitHub Issues on Project #2 with **Sprint** field.
- Minimize diff scope; match existing folder and naming conventions.
- Do not commit unless the user explicitly asks.

See [AGENTS.md](AGENTS.md) and [docs/ARCHITECTURE.md](docs/ARCHITECTURE.md).
